title: Ancient stolen relics returned to Lebanon
text:
Ancient stolen relics returned to Lebanon 1:33pm IST - 01:49 
Five ancient sculptures, carved between the fourth and sixth centuries BC, have been finally returned to Lebanon after being stolen in the country's civil war. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
